# Cloudflare Pages Routing

# IMPORTANT: Keep /web path accessible (don't redirect login)
# This must come BEFORE the catch-all redirects

# Redirect root domain to properties subdomain (except /web paths)
https://erposus.com/  https://properties.erposus.com/  301
http://erposus.com/  https://properties.erposus.com/  301

# Redirect www to properties subdomain
https://www.erposus.com/*  https://properties.erposus.com/:splat  301
http://www.erposus.com/*  https://properties.erposus.com/:splat  301

# SPA fallback (only for this site's pages)
/*  /index.html  200
